---

<section id="competitions" class="py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-left mb-20 max-w-3xl">
            <h2
                class="text-blue-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-4 text-sm md:text-base"
            >
                競技カテゴリー
            </h2>
            <h3
                class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-8"
            >
                Enjoy the Challenge!
            </h3>
            <p
                class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-500 leading-relaxed font-medium"
            >
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Amazing (A-MAZE-ing) -->
            <a
                href="/competitions/amazing"
                class="group relative bg-white border-4 border-black rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 aspect-[4/5] md:aspect-[3/4] block"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 p-10 flex flex-col justify-between z-10"
                >
                    <div>
                        <div
                            class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 overflow-hidden"
                        >
                            <img
                                src="/amazing-red-icon.jpg"
                                alt="a-MAZE-ing Challenge"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover p-2"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                            a-MAZE-ing Challenge
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-blue-500 font-medium text-lg">
                            アメージング！
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-blue-500 font-medium text-lg">
                            迷路を駆け抜けろ！
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <p
                        class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed opacity-0 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-500 delay-100"
                    >
                        迷路を攻略し、ゴールを目指す。<br
                        />正確な走行とセンサーの統合が鍵となるチャレンジ。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <!-- Abstract BG Shape -->
                <div
                    class="absolute -bottom-20 -right-20 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-100 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out opacity-50"
                >
                </div>
                <!-- Background Image (Visible) -->
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20 pointer-events-none mix-blend-multiply"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/amazing-green-icon.jpg"
                        alt=""
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                    />
                </div>
            </a>

            <!-- SumoBot (Centered) -->
            <a
                href="/competitions/sumobot"
                class="group relative bg-white border-4 border-black rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 aspect-[4/5] md:aspect-[3/4] block"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 p-10 flex flex-col justify-between z-10"
                >
                    <div>
                        <div
                            class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 overflow-hidden"
                        >
                            <img
                                src="/sumobot-red-icon.jpg"
                                alt="SumoBot"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover p-2"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                            SumoBot<br />Challenge
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-blue-500 font-medium text-lg">
                            スモーボット！
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-blue-500 font-medium text-lg">
                            押し出せ！
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <p
                        class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed opacity-0 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-500 delay-100"
                    >
                        相手を土俵から押し出す。<br
                        />自律的な力、センサーロジック、戦術的エンジニアリングの戦い。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <!-- Abstract BG Shape -->
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-48 h-48 bg-gray-100 rounded-full blur-2xl opacity-60"
                >
                </div>
                <!-- Background Image (Visible) -->
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20 pointer-events-none mix-blend-multiply"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/sumobot-detail-icon.jpg"
                        alt=""
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                    />
                </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Line Following -->
            <a
                href="/competitions/line-following"
                class="group relative bg-white border-4 border-black rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 aspect-[4/5] md:aspect-[3/4] block"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 p-10 flex flex-col justify-between z-10"
                >
                    <div>
                        <div
                            class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 overflow-hidden"
                        >
                            <img
                                src="/line-following-red-icon.jpg"
                                alt="Line Following"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover p-2"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                            Line Following Challenge
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-blue-400 font-medium text-lg">
                            ラインフォローイング！
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-blue-400 font-medium text-lg">
                            白黒ハッキリさせろ！
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <p
                        class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed opacity-0 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-500 delay-100"
                    >
                        ラインを攻略し、ピンポン玉を運ぶ。<br
                        />スピード、正確さ、繊細な制御が試される。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <!-- Abstract BG Shape -->
                <div
                    class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full bg-blue-50 opacity-50 rounded-full blur-3xl"
                >
                </div>
                <!-- Background Image (Visible) -->
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20 pointer-events-none mix-blend-multiply"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/line-following-detail-icon.jpg"
                        alt=""
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                    />
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
